1
00:00:56,920 --> 00:00:58,320
Just let the two of us in

2
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:00,600
No, what's wrong with you?

3
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,280
Let go, let me in now

4
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,800
Let me in, hurry, let me in

5
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,840
What's going on?

6
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,680
Quick, grab him

7
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,320
Zheng Yu, help me hold him down

8
00:01:20,320 --> 00:01:21,120
I can save him

9
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,960
Xiao Pang, sorry to trouble you

10
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,320
Xu Nan, quickly

11
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,520
He's still breathing

12
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:04,680
What did you make Lü Quan take?

13
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,560
Last time, when Lu Xin got into trouble

14
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:09,960
I smelled something strange

15
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:13,040
So I took some blood samples back to study

16
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,760
I found that he had actually been poisoned by a

17
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,560
strange poison called Soul-Bewitching Herb

18
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,520
Soul-Bewitching Herb?

19
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:20,880
Yes

20
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,840
This poison makes people lose their minds

21
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,040
and become highly aggressive

22
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:28,200
They'll even bite wildly like beasts

23
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:31,120
So afterward I consulted some medical texts

24
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,440
and made an antidote

25
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:35,240
So this is the truth of the fox spirit possession

26
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:38,880
Honored guests

27
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,520
Our young master has awakened

28
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:42,440
He wishes to meet his savior

29
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,280
All right

30
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,040
My apologies

31
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:48,240
Young Master said he only wants to see Fifth Concubine

32
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,200
This way, please

33
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:07,800
You've come

34
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,840
Young Master Lü, please stay seated

35
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,080
Don't force yourself

36
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,440
Young Master Lü

37
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,200
In several letters my elder sister wrote to me

38
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,960
she mentioned you every time

39
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,120
Back then, only you were willing to help her

40
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,840
I know you are not a bad man

41
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,440
So can you tell me

42
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,280
what exactly happened back then?

43
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,680
Do you know the Wang family had a thing

44
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,360
One time I drank too much

45
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,800
and wandered into the ruined house they used to hide it

46
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,360
That was where I met your sister

47
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,200
She told me to leave at once

48
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,680
But I would not listen

49
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,480
That thing suddenly rushed out and grabbed me

50
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,080
Luckily, your sister was there

51
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:58,120
Otherwise, I would have died at the Wang family estate

52
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,880
After that, whenever your sister was in trouble

53
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,960
I did all I could to help her

54
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,000
Until the time she came to me

55
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:11,520
Young Master Lü

56
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:12,720
Young Master Lü

57
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,720
Young Master Lü, I beg you, save me. What is it?

58
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,280
They...

59
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,760
They want to sacrifice me

60
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:18,360
I'm begging you. Sacrifice?

61
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,600
Save me, Young Master Lü

62
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,000
Take her back for me

63
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,920
Let go of me

64
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:28,000
Fourth Concubine has had a fever these past few days

65
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,120
She's delirious

66
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,240
Talking nonsense

67
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,040
Sorry for causing you trouble

68
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,840
Take her back

69
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,640
Make her take her medicine

70
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,640
No, I didn't, I'm not mad

71
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,560
He's the one who wants to kill me

72
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,240
He wants to kill me, Young Master Lü

73
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,320
You cannot take her away

74
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:41,960
What are you trying to do?

75
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,840
Let go of me

76
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,040
Master Wang, sorry to trouble you

77
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,400
I'll take her away now

78
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,680
Hold Lü Quan tight. Young Master Lü, save me

79
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,480
You cannot take her away, Young Master Lü

80
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,920
Let go of me. Please save me

81
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,360
Young Master Lü, save me

82
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,440
You watch as an innocent person is harmed

83
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,080
Do you have any conscience left?

84
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,800
Lock him up for me

85
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,200
You mean

86
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:08,520
my sister was sacrificed by the Wang family

87
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,160
If you keep staying with the Wang family

88
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,760
You'll die too

89
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,480
Yesterday, you told me

90
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,640
they make a sacrifice every three years

91
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,320
by my count, less than two months remain

92
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,320
I must find a way to expose their crimes

93
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,240
You want to be the bait

94
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:35,160
No, it's too dangerous

95
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,040
Our Lü family is already cursed

96
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,640
I've already become this wretched mess

97
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,120
I don't know when

98
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,840
I'll lose my life

99
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,200
Young Master Lü

100
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,400
You've been poisoned

101
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,560
Someone is using the curse as a cover

102
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,840
to frame your Lü family

103
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,960
This is the antidote I made. Keep it safe

104
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,080
Young Master Lü

105
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,040
If my elder sister were still alive

106
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,080
she would never want you to give up

107
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:12,040
She always believed you were a good man

108
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:29,200
My curse isn't over yet

109
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,680
No one better ruin my plans

110
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,840
Who is it

111
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,960
Master Ai, what brings you to my little shop so late

112
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,560
Is there something you need

113
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,320
No need to be so formal

114
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:49,880
I already know you quite well

115
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,280
I've been keeping an eye on you

116
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,480
Keeping an eye on me

117
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,520
I'm very interested in the Bone-collecting ritual

118
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,240
Brother Zheng Yu

119
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,080
I can call you brother, can't I

120
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,520
Can you teach me bone-collecting

121
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,040
Master Ai, you jest

122
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,160
What's so bad about being a feng shui master

123
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,120
You can make a fortune

124
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,360
and be held in high regard

125
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:11,800
Unlike us bone collectors

126
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,360
everyone keeps far away from us

127
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,280
and says we bring bad luck

128
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,680
Then what if I said

129
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:23,880
I'm very interested in you

130
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,640
Isn't this the Wang family's Fifth Concubine

131
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:38,000
What, does your Wang family need bone-collecting again

132
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,600
This is

133
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,880
Master Ai, the feng shui master

134
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:45,920
I've long heard of your great name

135
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:48,880
I didn't expect Master Ai to be a young lady

136
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,960
What are you doing here so late

137
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,600
Didn't Master Ai come this late as well

138
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,480
Am I disturbing you two

139
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:58,680
No

140
00:07:59,000 --> 00:07:59,800
Not at all

141
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,320
Not at all

142
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,880
So you two knew each other before

143
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,520
Xu Nan and I

144
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:13,520
often discuss medicinal principles with Fifth Concubine

145
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:16,520
and seek her advice on pharmacology

146
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,080
You really have no shame

147
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,960
So that's how it is

148
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:26,320
Brother Zheng Yu

149
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,680
We got so caught up talking just now

150
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,000
the tea's gone cold

151
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,760
Why not pour me another cup, brother

152
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,280
All right

153
00:08:42,920 --> 00:08:44,600
How attentive of you

154
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,520
I'll pour one for Fifth Concubine too

155
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,760
Fifth Concubine

156
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,800
Coming to see Brother Zheng Yu this late

157
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:53,520
is it because

158
00:08:53,520 --> 00:08:56,080
you want to speak to him alone about something private

159
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,200
Then I'll excuse myself

160
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,360
No need. I have nothing to say to him

161
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,880
I just mixed some antidote and brought it to you

162
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,200
I'm leaving

163
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:04,640
No, not you

164
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:15,880
Damn Zheng Yu, after only a few days apart

165
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:19,360
you're already making eyes at another young girl
